    <bioghist>Soldier with Co. F, 4th Michigan Infantry during the Civil War. He took part in twenty one battles and was wounded four times. At Gettysburg, he was wounded and taken prisoner by the Twenty-fourth Georgia Infantry, but he later escaped. After the war, he became an ornithologist.</bioghist>
